# Routes

Defined in `src/router/index.ts`. Auth guard redirects unauthenticated users to `Login`. `requiresSuperAdmin` meta redirects non-super-admins to `employees`.

## Public

| Path | Name | View |
|------|------|------|
| `/` | `home` | `views/HomeView.vue` |
| `/signup` | `signup` | `views/Signup.vue` |
| `/auth` | `auth` | `views/auth/AuthIndex.vue` (layout) |
| `/auth/login` | `Login` | `views/Login.vue` |
| `/auth/forgot-password` | `forgotPassword` | `views/ForgotPassword.vue` |
| `/auth/callback` | `Callback` | `views/auth/AuthCallback.vue` |
| `/auth/reset-password` | `resetPassword` | `views/auth/ResetPassword.vue` |

